        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>diced tomato</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 7-8 min or until the tomato has completely softened</p>",
