    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>courgette discs</strong> with the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 12-15 min, stirring continuously, or until the stock is almost fully absorbed and the orzo is cooked with a slight bite</p>",
