    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked through – this is your <strong>king prawn, tomato & courgette orzotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p><p>While the prawns are cooking, chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
